{"tid":815720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不是PTBF】想成為出租大叔，要符合什麼條件？","createTime":"2018-09-12T09:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T12:13:35.000Z","uid":3189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2af7241b447441a68179ace4e1dcf25b0e319a9a","tid":815720,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"西本貴信先生在2012年無心插柳地開始「出租大叔」這個副業，在日本造成極大迴響，各大媒體廣泛報道這個企劃，更令出租大叔這個業務迅速擴展；時至今天，「出租大叔」不再只有西本先生一人，日本全國都可以租借當地的大叔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/819957/org/5664de15c79a2fe08139383b70db9b79.jpg/kBXrJ78Tcgo9ROg5vgUrZ7vmOtI5tVzJ3kGOG95Bjhs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F819957%2Forg%2F5664de15c79a2fe08139383b70db9b79.jpg%2FkBXrJ78Tcgo9ROg5vgUrZ7vmOtI5tVzJ3kGOG95Bjhs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=92b75f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n企劃大受歡迎，西本先生現已榮升「出租大叔」的CEO，本人依然提供出租服務。(取自西本先生的個人官網)<br />\n<br />\n登入「出租大叔」的官方網站，隨即見到日本全國各地「出租大叔」的一張張大頭貼。點擊其中一張照片，就可以看到該位大叔的自我介紹──身高體重、職業興趣，以至想成為出租大叔的原因。無論你想租借哪一位大叔，價格一律每小時1000日元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/821718/org/9cc30021142cb862952059acac6ee36f.png/2EYcz3Xkbd6zxjCzXU3MPcJcvOLOhp8snTjt05047dM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F821718%2Forg%2F9cc30021142cb862952059acac6ee36f.png%2F2EYcz3Xkbd6zxjCzXU3MPcJcvOLOhp8snTjt05047dM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9f197222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在「出租大叔」的官網之中，可搜尋全日本各地的大叔，所有的價格一律每小時1000日元。<br />\n<br />\n目前，成功登記的「出租大叔」已超過80人，人人「賣點」不同。點擊以下圖片放大：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/821757/org/75bd4c4826d4184ff493545de6b8cb2a.png/8pUkCf0ua6uTHBIvekmavcbImuPTjPdIXDftuFw37bg?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F821757%2Forg%2F75bd4c4826d4184ff493545de6b8cb2a.png%2F8pUkCf0ua6uTHBIvekmavcbImuPTjPdIXDftuFw37bg%3Fv%3Dw640&h=e65d517e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【成為出租大叔的必要條件】<br />\n<br />\n根據官網介紹，要成為大叔須符合以下4項條件：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帥氣、令人意想不到的大叔<br />\n<br />\n希望全心全力為人打氣的大叔<br />\n<br />\n年齢 33歳以上62歳未満的大叔<br />\n<br />\n居住在日本的大叔（將來也可能招募海外的大叔）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為了保障顧客，申請成為大叔者，須與 CEO西本先生先進行面試審査，如果被委託人投訴3次，就會被解約。所以在官網上找到的出租大叔都有一定質素保證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出租大叔網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ossanrental.thebase.in/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fossanrental.thebase.in%2F&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c5f127e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://ossanrental.thebase.in/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/117775/%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFptbf-%E6%83%B3%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94-%E8%A6%81%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F117775%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AFptbf-%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258F%2594-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=512c9a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/117775/%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFptbf-%E6%83%B3%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94-%E8%A6%81%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"34e075e6fa09a268a15503d2756b8416cf86feea","tid":815720,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/kr7HfDB.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fkr7HfDB.jpg&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2bb36960\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/kr7HfDB.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/f